{"nId": "509", "userId": "6", "type": "0", "title": "", "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">HTML- Hyper Text Markup language, the mark up formatting language for the web</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Language to build web pages (document structure, content presentation). html</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"width: auto; height: auto; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">The &lt;html&gt;, &lt;head&gt;, &lt;title&gt;, and &lt;body&gt; elements must also be present in HTML</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'courier new'; box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\">+</font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 205); box-sizing: inherit;\">&lt;</span><font color=\"#a52a2a\">link</font><span style=\"color: red; box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;rel<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"stylesheet\"</span>&nbsp;type<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"text/css\"</span>&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"theme.css\"</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 205); box-sizing: inherit;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Consolas, 'courier new';\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><font face=\"Calibri\">+</font></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'courier new'; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'courier new'; color: rgb(165, 42, 42);\">img</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'courier new'; box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;src<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"smiley.gif\"</span>&nbsp;alt<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"Smiley face\"</span>&nbsp;height<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"42\"</span>&nbsp;width<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">=\"42\"</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'courier new'; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\">&gt;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt;\"><font color=\"#0000cd\" face=\"Consolas, courier new\">+&lt;p&gt;</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">XML ? extensible markup language, looks like HTML with no predefined tags, to store and to transfer data, XML tags are case sensitive and element must be properly nested<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">JSON(JavaScript Object Notation) ? alternate to XML, a subset of JavaScript programming language lightweight computer data interchangeable format and is language independent data format&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">Why do we need it? &nbsp;Information exchange: separate content from appearance, to store and transfer data, distributing data over the internet</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">Roles: HTML is to define the content of web pages<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CSS to specify the layout of the web pages<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;JavaScript to program the behavior of the web pages</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri;\">JavaScript: scripting language, nothing to do with Java, to interpreted language, scripts are executed without compilation, usually embedded in HTML and add interactivity to HTML pages</p><div>CSS: Cascading Style Sheets</div><div>Used to specify the layout of a web page.&nbsp;</div><div><button type=\"button\" class=\"close\" data-dismiss=\"modal\">\u00d7</button><div id=\"modal-text\" class=\"content modal-body\" placeholder=\"Enter text here...\" style=\"width: 598px;\">Client:<div><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><li>access to browser</li><li>visible codes</li><li>doesn't require server to create data</li></ul><div>Server:</div></div><div><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><li>access to server</li><li>invisible codes in page source</li><li>provides data to display on browser, not reside</li></ul></div></div></div>", "upVote": 0, "downVote": 0, "tags": ["HTML", "xml", "html", "json", "consolas", "enter", "client", "server", "css", "roles", "java", "javascript"], "favorite": false, "dateCreated": "2017-11-20 03:30:11", "dateModified": "2017-11-20 03:30:11"}